			<p align="left">Dear BAM and BET Trustees,</p>
			<div data-wfedit="html">
				<p align="left" style="text-align: left;" class=""><a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/07/19/arts/design/new-york-cultural-plan-museums.html?rref=collection%2Fsectioncollection%2Farts&action=click&contentCollection=arts&region=rank&module=package&version=highlights&contentPlacement=2&pgtype=sectionfront">The New York Times</a>					recently published an article on the city&#8217;s first &#8220;cultural plan&#8221; that will link future funding for arts organizations to their commitment to diversity. In a quote, I highlighted BAM's long commitment to diversity and our eagerness
					to make further strides. &#160;<br /></p>



				<p style="text-align: left;" align="left">The BAM Board News This Week will take some time off this summer. &#160;Please look for our next newsletter on Friday, Aug 25.&#160;</p>
			</div>
		</div>
