				<p style="text-align: left;" align="left"></p>
				<ul align="start">
					<li>You are cordially invited to the BAM Board Appreciation Dinner hosted by Diane & Adam E. Max on Monday, Sep 18, 2017 at The River Caf&#233;. Please join us on this special night to acknowledge trustee service and celebrate the 2017 Next Wave Festival.
						To RSVP, please contact <a href="mailto:patronservices@bam.org" target="_blank">Patron Services</a> at 718.636.4182.<br /></li>
