				<h3>BAMcin&#233;matek presents three film series opening this week and next:</h3></div>
		</div>
		<div data-wfcb="text" data-wflabel="Text" class="text-block" draggable="false">
			<div data-wfedit="html">
				<p align="center" style="text-align: left;" class="alt"><br /></p>
				<p align="center" style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/animation-block-party-2017">Animation Block Party 2017</a> (Jul 28-30). Returning for its 14<sup>th</sup> annual edition, this premier festival showcases something for everyone: a clever comedy like <i><a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/bee-movie">Bee
Movie</a></i> (Jul 30), an inside look at <a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/cartoon-network-shorts">Cartoon Network Shorts</a> (Jul 30), and a round-up of family-friendly programming in <a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/animation-for-kids">Animation
for Kids</a> (Jul 29).</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div data-wfcb="image" data-wflabel="Image" class="image-block" draggable="false" id="image-block-1502903061647">
