				<p align="left" style="text-align: left;" class=""><a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/in-concert" class="">In Concert</a> (Jul 31-Aug 13). These outstanding concert films capture iconic pop culture moments from Jay Z&#8217;s <a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/fade-to-black">Fade
to Black</a> (Jul 31) to Bjork&#8217;s <a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/bjork-biophilia-live">Biophilia Live</a> (Aug 3). <br /></p>
			</div>
