					films that set him apart like <i><a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/philadelphia">Philadelphia</a></i> (Aug 6-16), <i><a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/the-manchurian-candidate">The Manchurian Candidate</a></i> (Aug 7), and <i><a href="http://www.bam.org/film/2017/the-silence-of-the-lambs">The Silence of the Lambs</a> </i>(Aug
