			<div data-wfedit="html">
				<p align="left" class="" style="text-align: left;">In Conjunction with BAM Education, <a href="dancemotionusa.org">DanceMotion USA<sup>SM</sup></a> welcomed 5 international artists and arts managers this week from the Dominican Republic, Ethiopia, Thailand, and Tunisia as part of our Professional
					Development Program (PDP). Creative Capital led a 4-day workshop focusing on&#160;verbal communications, marketing, promotion, and&#160;web essentials,&#160;and&#160;paired them with a NYC&#160;artist.&#160;The program also included movement workshops
					taught by Larry Keigwin, Reggie Wilson, and John Heginbotham,&#160;and an informal showing of participants&#8217; work.<br /></p>
